@startuml
title Cloud Food Corner

actor Customer
participant "Browser / Web App" as Web
participant "Spring MVC Controller" as API
participant "Thymeleaf View" as View
database "Future DB" as DB

Customer -> Web : Open home page
Web -> API : GET /api
note right of API
Current implemented endpoint:
- GET /api
end note

API -> View : return "home"
View --> Web : Render home.html
Web --> Customer : Show welcome page

== Future Planned APIs ==
Web -> API : GET /menu
API -> DB : Fetch menu items
DB --> API : Menu data
API --> Web : JSON / rendered data

Web -> API : POST /cart
API --> Web : Cart updated

Web -> API : POST /checkout
API --> Web : Order confirmation
@enduml